    "V_c": 0.13,
    "V_v": 0.04,
    "\u03c4_d": 0.5714
  },
  "stability_notes": "dt=0.025 ensures CFL condition for explicit Laplacian (D\u00b7dt/dx\u00b2 \u2248 0.66 < 1). Piecewise conditions evaluated with exact threshold comparisons.",
